        "## Data-Driven Design Enables Generative User Interfaces\n",
        "\n",
        "There are many partially overlapping design terms created by different people for diverse purposes. Design vocabulary may be created for distinguishing a particular type of design from another - or to market oneself as the creator of the word.\n",
